yingyinNormal.en: Tree frogs can modulate their infrared output. We used strands from their DNA to adapt her to a tropical climate. But I never imagined...
yingyinNormal.zh: 树蛙能控制红外线输出，我们提取了一些它们的DNA帮助她适应热带气候，但是我从没想到…

yingyinNormal.en: Bugayev is telling me that they are willing to reduce their oil output by another 20% by the first of next month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布加耶夫告诉我他们愿意在下月1日之前再减产20%的原油。

yingyinNormal.en: Forget everything that you've ever heard or seen on television. Attempts to manipulate the data output are futile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 忘记你在电视上听见过或看见过的一切，企图操控数据结果都是徒劳。

yingyinNormal.en: It would take more than 4 million cows to equal the output of just one nuclear power plant. But maybe that's not the point.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那将需要四百多万头牛，才能与一个核能计划的产量持平。但这也许不是重点。

yingyinNormal.en: While I disagree with the premise of tenure, if they gave it to me, it wouldn't diminish my output. You know, I'm like the sun. Can't turn this off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然我不太认同终身教职制度，但如果他们给我这职位，我也会继续对科学界做贡献，我就跟太阳一样发光发热，停不下来。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
